description: A new majority Black and Latinx-owned and operated digital bank hopes to make supporting Black-owned banks and businesses a little easier for consumers.
source.name: CNN

author: Mallika Kallingal, CNN
title: A woman's inspiring journey from janitor to health care worker
description: When Jaines Andrades started working at Baystate Medical in in Springfield, Massachusetts, she was a janitor. But she worked her way through nursing school. And now ten years later she has returned as a nurse practitioner.
source.name: CNN

title: Kim Jong Un gets emotional over North Korea's Covid efforts
description: Kim Jong Un choked up before praising North Korea's "anti-epidemic" efforts and unveiling a new ballistic missile at a military parade in Pyongyang. Neither Kim, nor any crowd members appeared to be wearing masks.
source.name: CNN

title: ER doctor: This is extraordinarily inept in terms of public health
description: President Trump, in his first public event since he was diagnosed with coronavirus, gave a brief, campaign-style speech from the balcony of the White House.
source.name: CNN

author: Giulia Heyward and Kelly McCleary, CNN
title: NFL encourages players to come out in new PSA for National Coming Out Day
description: The NFL is celebrating National Coming Out Day with a video featuring openly gay and bisexual former players encouraging current LGBTQ players to come out.
source.name: CNN
